experiment arcHeating
instrument HEA
start 2003 11 19 1700
end 2003 11 19 2200
status R
description Modification of conductivity near auroral arcs using Heating
contact Thomas Leyser
email tbl@irfu.se
operator Mike Rietveld
submitter Thomas Leyser
resources Sw(31)
notes
Modification of ionospheric conductivity near quiet auroral arcs. Detection 
with EISCAT UHF and ALIS (optical emissions). Needs clear skyes. In case of no 
aurora but ionospheric critical frequency above 4 MHz the backup experiment is
to study Heating-induced luminescence.
